      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "Since we had no reliable data for this future mode, we simply assumed that the conditions of an AMOD service are comparable to the existing mode \"car as passenger\". In both modes, travelers do not have control over the car and drive with other travelers. Further, we had to define costs for the mode \"car as passenger\", since it is originally assumed as complimentary. [CITATION_1] estimated a cost reduction per mile driven of up to 30% for an AMOD fleet with middle sized sedan cars and up to 60% for an AMOD fleet of small cars."
